  "lore": {
    "key": "Tbl_Unit_Desc_68",
    "english": "Demon. An oni from the demon realm currently living in the human world after being banished from her home. After coming to the human world, she's being hunted by Taimanin, UFS, and the Chinese Union alike. However, she's the sort of person who can become friends with anyone, regardless of their background, as long as they both see eye-to-eye. Enjoys liquor a little too much, even for Oni's standards. She also likes gyaru-style fashion, but is frustrated because no one else around her sees her fashion the same way.\n\nPossesses the physical abilities of an oni and uses both a machine gun and a large club with ease. She also leads a criminal organization called \"Francis Family\", consisting of gangsters who fell head over heels for her beauty, rapidly expanding its size.",
    "japanese": "Demon. An oni from the demon realm currently living in the human world after being banished from her home. After coming to the human world, she's being hunted by Taimanin, UFS, and the Chinese Union alike. However, she's the sort of person who can become friends with anyone, regardless of their background, as long as they both see eye-to-eye. Enjoys liquor a little too much, even for Oni's standards. She also likes gyaru-style fashion, but is frustrated because no one else around her sees her fashion the same way.\n\nPossesses the physical abilities of an oni and uses both a machine gun and a large club with ease. She also leads a criminal organization called \"Francis Family\", consisting of gangsters who fell head over heels for her beauty, rapidly expanding its size.",
    "korean": "Demon. An oni from the demon realm currently living in the human world after being banished from her home. After coming to the human world, she's being hunted by Taimanin, UFS, and the Chinese Union alike. However, she's the sort of person who can become friends with anyone, regardless of their background, as long as they both see eye-to-eye. Enjoys liquor a little too much, even for Oni's standards. She also likes gyaru-style fashion, but is frustrated because no one else around her sees her fashion the same way.\n\nPossesses the physical abilities of an oni and uses both a machine gun and a large club with ease. She also leads a criminal organization called \"Francis Family\", consisting of gangsters who fell head over heels for her beauty, rapidly expanding its size.",
    "chinese_simplified": "Demon. An oni from the demon realm currently living in the human world after being banished from her home. After coming to the human world, she's being hunted by Taimanin, UFS, and the Chinese Union alike. However, she's the sort of person who can become friends with anyone, regardless of their background, as long as they both see eye-to-eye. Enjoys liquor a little too much, even for Oni's standards. She also likes gyaru-style fashion, but is frustrated because no one else around her sees her fashion the same way.\n\nPossesses the physical abilities of an oni and uses both a machine gun and a large club with ease. She also leads a criminal organization called \"Francis Family\", consisting of gangsters who fell head over heels for her beauty, rapidly expanding its size.",
    "chinese_traditional": "Demon. An oni from the demon realm currently living in the human world after being banished from her home. After coming to the human world, she's being hunted by Taimanin, UFS, and the Chinese Union alike. However, she's the sort of person who can become friends with anyone, regardless of their background, as long as they both see eye-to-eye. Enjoys liquor a little too much, even for Oni's standards. She also likes gyaru-style fashion, but is frustrated because no one else around her sees her fashion the same way.\n\nPossesses the physical abilities of an oni and uses both a machine gun and a large club with ease. She also leads a criminal organization called \"Francis Family\", consisting of gangsters who fell head over heels for her beauty, rapidly expanding its size.",
    "spanish": "Demon. An oni from the demon realm currently living in the human world after being banished from her home. After coming to the human world, she's being hunted by Taimanin, UFS, and the Chinese Union alike. However, she's the sort of person who can become friends with anyone, regardless of their background, as long as they both see eye-to-eye. Enjoys liquor a little too much, even for Oni's standards. She also likes gyaru-style fashion, but is frustrated because no one else around her sees her fashion the same way.\n\nPossesses the physical abilities of an oni and uses both a machine gun and a large club with ease. She also leads a criminal organization called \"Francis Family\", consisting of gangsters who fell head over heels for her beauty, rapidly expanding its size."
